#: ../../../dev-guide/docs.rst:83
msgid ""
"If you'd like to rebuild the documentation from scratch. This is normally "
"not necessary since Sphinx will detect and only build the required changes. "
"But if you are running into strange errors you may want to try this. The "
"following command will wipe all generated files."
msgstr ""
"Si vous souhaitez reconstruire la documentation depuis le début. Cela n'est "
"normalement pas nécessaire car Sphinx détectera et ne construira que les "
"modifications requises. Mais si vous rencontrez des erreurs étranges, vous "
"pouvez essayer ceci. La commande suivante supprimera tous les fichiers "
"générés."

#: ../../../dev-guide/docs.rst:88
msgid "$ make clean"
msgstr "$ make clean"

#: ../../../dev-guide/docs.rst:90
msgid ""
"Sphinx can also build documentation as a PDF but this requires latex to be "
